iaik.pkcs.pkcs11.wrapper
Interface PKCS11Constants

public interface PKCS11Constants

This interface holds constants of the PKCS#11 v2.11 standard. This is mainly the content of the 'pkcs11t.h' header file. Mapping of primitiv data types to Java types: 

   TRUE .......................................... true
   FALSE ......................................... false
   CK_BYTE ....................................... byte
   CK_CHAR ....................................... char
   CK_UTF8CHAR ................................... char
   CK_BBOOL ...................................... boolean
   CK_ULONG ...................................... long
   CK_LONG ....................................... long
   CK_FLAGS ...................................... long
   CK_NOTIFICATION ............................... long
   CK_SLOT_ID .................................... long
   CK_SESSION_HANDLE ............................. long
   CK_USER_TYPE .................................. long
   CK_SESSION_HANDLE ............................. long
   CK_STATE ...................................... long
   CK_OBJECT_HANDLE .............................. long
   CK_OBJECT_CLASS ............................... long
   CK_HW_FEATURE_TYPE ............................ long
   CK_KEY_TYPE ................................... long
   CK_CERTIFICATE_TYPE ........................... long
   CK_ATTRIBUTE_TYPE ............................. long
   CK_VOID_PTR ................................... Object[]
   CK_BYTE_PTR ................................... byte[]
   CK_CHAR_PTR ................................... char[]
   CK_UTF8CHAR_PTR ............................... char[]
   CK_MECHANISM_TYPE ............................. long
   CK_RV ......................................... long
   CK_RSA_PKCS_OAEP_MGF_TYPE ..................... long
   CK_RSA_PKCS_OAEP_SOURCE_TYPE .................. long
   CK_RC2_PARAMS ................................. long
   CK_MAC_GENERAL_PARAMS ......................... long
   CK_EXTRACT_PARAMS ............................. long
   CK_PKCS5_PBKD2_PSEUDO_RANDOM_FUNCTION_TYPE .... long
   CK_PKCS5_PBKDF2_SALT_SOURCE_TYPE .............. long
   CK_EC_KDF_TYPE ................................ long
   CK_X9_42_DH_KDF_TYPE .......................... long
